***UPDATE***Seller Concessions $3000

Discover the perfect blend of convenience and comfort in this 4-bed, 2.5-bath gem just 17 minutes from Uptown Charlotte. Ideal proximity with 10 minutes to Mint Hill, 14 minutes to South Park Mall, and a short 35-minute drive to the serene Lake Wylie. Enjoy swift access to the airport within 25 minutes. This home offers not just a residence, but a lifestyle—situated amidst a consortium of community amenities. Your ideal location awaits!
